=I'm doing seo, in the following list, remove the keyword that is not related to "{{ $('Get Job').item.json['Primary Keywords'] }}"

{{ $json['Related Keywords'] }}

Return in an array for the remaining keywords, remember don't change any words and keep case-sensitive, your json:

parameters.jsCode:
return {
  data: $input.all().map((inputItem, batchIndex) => {
    const keyword = $("Edit Fields").all()[batchIndex].json.keyword;
    const slicedItems = inputItem.json.items.slice(0, 1);

    return slicedItems.map(entry => ({
      ...entry,
      batchIndex,
      keyword
    }));
  }).flat()
};

